# Ms.Underdog Mobile Detailing - Local Environment Variables
# --------------------------------------------------------

# Email Integration (via Web3Forms - https://web3forms.com)
# To receive booking requests directly in your inbox:
# 1. Visit https://web3forms.com and enter your email.
# 2. Copy the access key emailed to you.
# 3. Create a local '.env' file in this directory and paste the key below:
VITE_WEB3FORMS_ACCESS_KEY=your_web3forms_access_key_here
